# WASM build outputs (generated by wasm-pack). wasm-pack also writes its own
# src/wasm/.gitignore ("*") that ignores everything here, including the stub.
# The type stub (rosette_wasm.d.ts) is nonetheless committed (force-added once)
# as a checked-in cache, so the app can be type-checked locally without a Rust +
# wasm-pack toolchain; git keeps tracked files regardless of ignore rules. CI
# rebuilds wasm and fails if the committed stub is stale (see the `app` job in
# .github/workflows/ci.yml). After regenerating, stage it with: git add -f.
src/wasm/

# Tauri build outputs
src-tauri/target/
src-tauri/gen/
